author: dandiep
msg: Make SwaInInterceptor a bit more robust. Any attachment that has an index greater than the list size can simply be appended to the end of the list. This prevents conflicts with the HolderInInterceptor. Attachments which have an index less than the list size can be inserted.

author: psmith
msg: Adds an option that determines whether a new thread, or the existing thread
is used to import the events into the Receiver. By default the behaviour remains
unchanged with a new Thread created to manage the import.
The new Thread that is created has a custom Thread name to differentiate it from other threads.
